HEADWORD: Re-presentation
<hw>Re-pres`en*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(r?-prez`?n-t?"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[See <er>Re-present</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of re-presenting, or
